<%
  title = 'ProConnect - Professional Network';
%>

<!-- Compose -->
<div class="li-card">
  <div class="li-post-box">
    <div class="li-post-avatar">SR</div>
    <button class="li-post-input">Start a post, try writing an article</button>
  </div>
  <div class="li-post-actions">
    <a href="#" class="li-post-action video"><i class="bi bi-camera-video-fill"></i> Video</a>
    <a href="#" class="li-post-action photo"><i class="bi bi-image-fill"></i> Photo</a>
    <a href="#" class="li-post-action article"><i class="bi bi-pencil-square"></i> Write article</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- POST 1 — Company Award -->
<div class="li-card" style="margin-top:8px;">
  <div class="post-header">
    <div class="post-author">
      <div class="post-logo" style="background:#0a66c2;border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;">CC</div>
      <div>
        <div class="post-author-name">Castrosasz Convertiblessd Pvt Ltd</div>
        <div class="post-author-meta">24,391 followers</div>
        <div class="post-author-time"><span>2d</span> <i class="bi bi-globe2" style="font-size:11px;"></i></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-controls">
      <button><i class="bi bi-three-dots"></i></button>
      <button><i class="bi bi-x-lg" style="font-size:16px;"></i></button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="post-body">
    🎉 Thrilled to announce that <a href="#">Castrosasz Convertiblessd</a> has been recognized as one of India's <strong>Top 50 Emerging Tech Companies of 2026!</strong><br><br>
    This milestone belongs to every person who showed up, solved hard problems, and believed in our mission. From Jaipur to the global stage — we're just getting started! 🚀
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a66c2,#00b09b);">
    <img src="/images/post-image-1.png" alt="Post Image">
  </div>
  <div class="post-footer">
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up"></i> Like</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-chat"></i> Comment</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-repeat"></i> Repost</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-send"></i> Send</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- POST 2 — Chad L. Allen -->
<div class="li-card" style="margin-top:8px;">
  <div class="post-header">
    <div class="post-author">
      <div class="post-logo" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f093fb,#f5576c);">CA</div>
      <div>
        <div class="post-author-name">Chad L. Allen</div>
        <div class="post-author-meta">Full-Stack Developer at CloudBurst Technologies</div>
        <div class="post-author-time"><span>5h</span> <i class="bi bi-globe2" style="font-size:11px;"></i></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-controls">
      <button><i class="bi bi-three-dots"></i></button>
      <button><i class="bi bi-x-lg" style="font-size:16px;"></i></button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="post-body" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
    Join us for an exciting event packed with insights, networking, and innovation. Connect with professionals, explore new ideas, and be part of the future of technology. 🚀
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a66c2,#00b09b);">
    <img src="/images/post-image-2.png" alt="Post Image">
  </div>
  <div class="post-footer">
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up"></i> Like</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-chat"></i> Comment</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-repeat"></i> Repost</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-send"></i> Send</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- POST 3 — Event -->
<div class="li-card" style="margin-top:8px;">
  <div class="post-header">
    <div class="post-author">
      <div class="post-logo" style="background:#e91e8c;border-radius:8px;font-size:11px;font-weight:800;">RJ</div>
      <div>
        <div class="post-author-name">Roger C. Jimenez</div>
        <div class="post-author-meta">12,004 followers</div>
        <div class="post-author-time"><span>6h</span> <i class="bi bi-globe2" style="font-size:11px;"></i></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="post-controls">
      <button><i class="bi bi-three-dots"></i></button>
      <button><i class="bi bi-x-lg" style="font-size:16px;"></i></button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="post-body" style="margin-bottom:10px;">
    We're excited to bring together innovators, developers, and industry leaders for an engaging experience filled with learning and networking opportunities. This event will showcase the latest trends in technology, product development, and digital transformation. Join us to connect with like-minded professionals, gain valuable insights, and be part of something impactful. 🚀
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a66c2,#00b09b);">
    <img src="/images/post-image-3.png" alt="Post Image">
  </div>
  <div class="post-footer">
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-hand-thumbs-up"></i> Like</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-chat"></i> Comment</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-repeat"></i> Repost</button>
    <button class="post-action-btn"><i class="bi bi-send"></i> Send</button>
  </div>
</div>